snippet.title: Fit in Six: Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for exercise and to improve your health with the new game Fit in Six. Getting in shape and fitness is now fun on the Nintendo Wii.

IGN's YouTube is just a taste of our content. Get more:
